igure>; &lt;p id=&quot;5n0lcX&quot;>;几个月前，苹果推出了最新一批智能手表，推出了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/23878981/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-review-double-tap- precision-finding-siri&quot;>;Apple Watch Ultra 2&lt;/a>;（799 美元）以及新款 &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/23878981/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-review-double-tap- precision-finding-siri&quot;>;Apple Watch Series 9&lt;/a>;（399 美元）。每款可穿戴设备都有自己的优点和缺点，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23369207/apple-watch-se-2022-review-smartwatch&quot;>;第二代 Apple Watch SE&lt;/ a>;（249 美元），但新款可穿戴设备的推出也意味着现在市场上的 Apple Watch 型号比以往任何时候都多，而且还有更多优惠。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float -left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;CWUc7k&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;如何选择购买哪款 Apple Watch&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23037217/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-second-gen-se-best-smartwatch-how- to&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;目前最优惠的 AirPods&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21302051/best-apple-airpods-deals&quot;},{&quot;title&quot; :&quot;如何安装 watchOS 10&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23879092/watchos-10-install-how-to&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt; /div>; &lt;p id=&quot;sHcaqK&quot;>;但是有了所有这些选项，您应该选择哪一个？一般来说，您希望购买您能买得起的最新款手表，以便它能够继续接收来自 Apple 的软件更新。最新更新 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23786155/watchos-10-preview-apple-watch&quot;>;watchOS 10&lt;/a>; 刚刚在 Apple Watch Series 4 及更新版本上推出，尽管没有人能肯定地说Series 4是否会成为下一个...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21289209/best-apple-watch-deals&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/21289209/best-apple-watch-deals" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/21289209/best-apple-watch-deals</id><author><name>布兰登·威德</name><name>卡梅伦·福克纳</name></author></entry></feed>